Power with Purpose 2017

At Devex, we're committed to celebrating women leaders in our industry. That's why we've once again partnered with McKinsey & Company to tell the stories of five remarkable women through Power with Purpose, our leadership recognition campaign. Help us celebrate women leaders in global development, and share #PowerWithPurpose: http://powerwithpurpose.devex.com

Publicado por Devex en Jueves, 22 de junio de 2017
